{"tid":1903997,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"文宣貼巴士站撐言論自由","createTime":"2020-02-29T10:38:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-29T11:52:05.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e24029f598769bd0cba274c95846b192dda58709","tid":1903997,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T10:38:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200229/QF7DMRPTUIFF64P2H54DYAJELE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200229%2FQF7DMRPTUIFF64P2H54DYAJELE%2F&d=OftESTy%2BPOS3A4jdltYT2zWqReVd2N9LFFOFvvIGphw%3D&h=379f3c63\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200229%2FQF7DMRPTUIFF64P2H54DYAJELE%2F&h=7c7107e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200229/QF7DMRPTUIFF64P2H54DYAJELE/</a><br />\n<br />\n文宣貼巴士站撐言論自由<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200229/large/1582899383_8260.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200229%2Flarge%2F1582899383_8260.jpg&h=0483a116&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n油麻地警署附近巴士站被貼上單張，力撐《頭條新聞》代表言論自由。<br />\n<br />\n王喜在《頭條新聞》客串扮演「忠勇毅」主持《驚方訊息》環節，寸盡警方抗疫時的荒誕表現，首集播出後大受網民支持，但警務處處長卻向廣播處長梁家榮發出投訴信施「施壓」，不過《頭條》未受影響，上周五播出的第二集依然寸盡警務處處長「PK鄧」鄧炳強。《蘋果》記者昨日在油麻地警署附近巴士站，發現有人貼出黑白單張力撐《頭條》。<br />\n<br />\n單張中有警察公共關係科總警司郭嘉銓和「忠勇毅」王喜的照片，當中寫着︰「為甚麼警方要針對一個時事節目，因為《頭條新聞》代表了言論自由。節目基於事實，以嬉笑怒罵形式諷刺時弊，批評和監督政府施政。」此外還有︰「沒有言論自由，政府封鎖消息，剩下官方資訊，沒有言論自由，人民無法批評，政府不受監控，最終成為暴政一言堂，所以撐港台、撐《頭條新聞》。」<br />\n<br />\n採訪：如文"},{"pid":"6115ec086f9d0beaa3d540bd55061f0fb0f977e7","tid":1903997,"uid":53172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T10:39:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4a16444cd9d04c9aaa591dec8bad24f99510a4ff","tid":1903997,"uid":127807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T11:51:26.000Z","msg":"有計"},{"pid":"8c468c7527803555f976c7caf0002f775e5de5ad","tid":1903997,"uid":127807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T11:52:05.000Z","msg":"不過貼時要小心休班狗"}]}